the types of flies that came

00:20:37.160 --> 00:20:39.160
in and out of the windows.

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:40.680
End quote.

00:20:40.680 --> 00:20:44.250
Later, as Jaime is briefed
on details of the case,

00:20:44.250 --> 00:20:47.590
