with the observation

00:20:47.590 --> 00:20:52.420
that his superior has one brown
shoe lace and one black one.

00:20:52.420 --> 00:20:56.770
The style of his speech
reveals a clear allusion

00:20:56.770 --> 00:20:58.750
to the step-by-step
reasoning typical

00:20:58.750 --> 00:21:02.190 position:56%
