side, to stand next to him.

00:21:08.910 --> 00:21:12.120
He even bent down, to get a
closer look, and then straightened

00:21:12.120 --> 00:21:14.350
up with a triumphant smile.

00:21:14.350 --> 00:21:16.250
This is what I think
happened, chief.

00:21:16.250 --> 00:21:18.940
Actually, both shoelaces are brown.

00:21:18.940 --> 00:21:21.260 position:56%
Only one received some black polish.

00:21:21.260 --> 00:21:23.610
Probably when you were
shining your shoes.

00:21:23.610 --> 00:21:26.540
Did you do that yourself, chief,
with one of those little bottles,

00:21:26.540 --> 00:21:29.620
