the little sponge at the tip?

00:21:29.620 --> 00:21:31.960
Jaime Bunda went back to
sit comfortable in front

00:21:31.960 --> 00:21:35.170
of his superior, who could
not stop looking at his shoes,

00:21:35.170 --> 00:21:38.330
and then at his subordinate,
completely dumbfounded.

00:21:38.330 --> 00:21:40.610
His authority undermined.

00:21:40.610 --> 00:21:42.240
End quote.

00:21:42.240 --> 00:21:45.210
The joke, of course, is not
just that Jaime is forced

00:21:45.210 --> 00:21:48.620
to exercise his considerable
observational skills

00:21:48.620 --> 00:21:51.500
on exaggeratedly trivial matters.

00:21:51.500 --> 00:21:54.800
But that he is entirely
unable to distinguish trivial

00:21:54.800 --> 00:21:58.820
or irrelevant observations
from important clues.

00:21:58.820 --> 00:22:02.310
Well, in a Sherlock Holmes story,
such an episode might serve

00:22:02.310 --> 00:22:05.960 position:56%
to demonstrate the detective's skill
in advance of a brilliant deduction

00:22:05.960 --> 00:22:10.970
that solves the crime, Jaime Bunda
equally enthusiastically pursues

00:22:10.970 --> 00:22:13.260
leads that are related to the case,

00:22:13.260 --> 00:22:16.810
and others that just match
patterns he has read about.

00:22:16.810 --> 00:22:20.850 position:56%
