repeats several times throughout the

00:22:20.850 --> 00:22:24.600
novel, quoting Alexandre
Dumas, but then he never tracks

00:22:24.600 --> 00:22:26.230
down the one female character

00:22:26.230 --> 00:22:29.340
who holds the most
important information.

00:22:29.340 --> 00:22:33.070
It might well be said that if the
murder is largely without clues

00:22:33.070 --> 00:22:37.430
that lead us, as readers, to its
conclusion, the novel is replete

00:22:37.430 --> 00:22:39.840
with clues, like the
mismatched shoes laces,

00:22:39.840 --> 00:22:42.840
