00:23:09.560 --> 00:23:11.180
to begin with Conan Doyle.

00:23:11.180 --> 00:23:12.900
Which is always where to begin.

00:23:12.900 --> 00:23:16.370 position:56%
Right? However, I argue that the way

00:23:16.370 --> 00:23:20.030
that Pepetela satirizes the
detective style also points

00:23:20.030 --> 00:23:21.780
to another literary source,

00:23:21.780 --> 00:23:25.670
