kind of counterfeit.

00:27:31.790 --> 00:27:34.950
Just like the readers of
the 19th century novel.

00:27:34.950 --> 00:27:38.430
And explicitly attributing the
sources of Jaime Bunda's style

00:27:38.430 --> 00:27:42.790 position:56%
